'''俄勒岡波特蘭聖殿'''（Portland Oregon Temple）是一座[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]的聖殿。2014年，俄勒岡波特蘭聖殿迎來了其開幕25週年紀念<ref name=Toone>{{cite news|last1=Toone|first1=Trent|title=LDS Church's Portland Oregon Temple turns 25|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865608234/LDS-Churchs-Portland-Oregon-Temple-turns-25.html?pg=all|accessdate=26 April 2015|publisher=Deseret News|date=7 August 2014|archive-date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022001114/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865608234/LDS-Churchs-Portland-Oregon-Temple-turns-25.html?pg=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Newell>{{cite news|last1=Newell|first1=Cliff|title=Reaching toward heaven, reaching out to people|url=http://portlandtribune.com/pt/9-news/231769-95318-reaching-toward-heaven-reaching-out-to-people|accessdate=26 April 2015|publisher=Portland Tribune|date=28 August 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050646/http://portlandtribune.com/pt/9-news/231769-95318-reaching-toward-heaven-reaching-out-to-people|dead-url=no}}</ref>。波特蘭聖殿是耶穌基督後期聖徒教會在俄勒岡州的首個聖殿。2012年，聖殿新設了遊客中心。

